  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forgotten mechs have awoken in their underground bases. Now they must continue their unfinished battle. Do you have the skill to operate them? Try it in this quick 2D action game for two players. Arm your weapons and destroy the enemy!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon has a distinct characteristics and you can only equip two of them. Every combination requires a different play style. Choose what best suits your mood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/c228ff2f055cbca169ba2416264e2fe6.poster.avif?t=1732262877\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/c228ff2f055cbca169ba2416264e2fe6.webm?t=1732262877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/c228ff2f055cbca169ba2416264e2fe6.mp4?t=1732262877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mech's legs and head rotate independently. You can walk in one direction and shoot in another. The game is best enjoyed when playing with controllers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/2eea0baf4dded14fbb5ee0e7a80b00cb.poster.avif?t=1732262877\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/2eea0baf4dded14fbb5ee0e7a80b00cb.webm?t=1732262877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/2eea0baf4dded14fbb5ee0e7a80b00cb.mp4?t=1732262877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forgotten mechs have awoken in their underground bases. Now they must continue their unfinished battle. Do you have the skill to operate them? Try it in this quick 2D action game for two players. Arm your weapons and destroy the enemy!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon has a distinct characteristics and you can only equip two of them. Every combination requires a different play style. Choose what best suits your mood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/c228ff2f055cbca169ba2416264e2fe6.poster.avif?t=1732262877\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/c228ff2f055cbca169ba2416264e2fe6.webm?t=1732262877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/c228ff2f055cbca169ba2416264e2fe6.mp4?t=1732262877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mech's legs and head rotate independently. You can walk in one direction and shoot in another. The game is best enjoyed when playing with controllers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/2eea0baf4dded14fbb5ee0e7a80b00cb.poster.avif?t=1732262877\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/2eea0baf4dded14fbb5ee0e7a80b00cb.webm?t=1732262877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2749090/extras/2eea0baf4dded14fbb5ee0e7a80b00cb.mp4?t=1732262877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
